title: Doomed minion
body: I still have not received the Doomed minion Icon. I really desperately want that Icon as I think it is the best in the game :(

replies.body: Teemoing icons should be done distributing now.  If you are still missing one, reach out to us in a [support ticket](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new). We'll be happy to take a look at your specific issue!
